{"tid":17241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲出智慧齒會發燒","createTime":"2016-12-01T18:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T16:01:27.000Z","uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3bafcd8d1ad5091bab60b644740aee9aafb3ae","tid":17241,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"呢幾日智慧齒個位既牙肉腫腫地<br />\n我都加強左清潔用飲多左水<br />\n但岩岩沖完涼後突然頭暈同想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲好似有少少發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食左感冒藥好左少少但都係瞓唔到覺<br />\n聽日仲要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享下出智慧齒既經驗"},{"pid":"d3c63cfcb1d608801100eb630e2be31bac1b8a61","tid":17241,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"發炎所以發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd84dc5e79d4688b8e22b0a03efbaa4e14e6c9e","tid":17241,"uid":1954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發炎所以發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢一刻好想剝左隻智慧齒一了百了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n智慧齒根本係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b71ab5d3f1c1fced12dc0385d3fdfc64588efdb","tid":17241,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"好臭"},{"pid":"a7f0428bf9e8e8017bb1644c5a34c91fd36118ed","tid":17241,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:30:33.000Z","msg":"妊娠症狀"},{"pid":"fc83858443a23dbf972d74d1084ee13e1a963529","tid":17241,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>妊娠症狀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通我單性繁殖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67070bbf4cd866231946baba8fd167a0c2039cdc","tid":17241,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇左牙醫，要約時間剝喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49af3037ecaa29721673ac836603514edf3b4f3a","tid":17241,"uid":68370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"出左 但無發過燒"},{"pid":"2995d76a73f6a5635134d505ab7f7a15e8c2575e","tid":17241,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左 但無發過燒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果次係因為發炎而發燒<br />\n我上個星期去剝隻智慧齒<br />\n反而剝完牙冇發燒"},{"pid":"ba9977ad243d8f1385423c02d1f31115be60918c","tid":17241,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"成日到牙鉸附近啲牙肉 有排先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02e3ec6671adf30a5b15eb94f0dd03c285cc770","tid":17241,"uid":68370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出左 但無發過燒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果次係因為發炎而發燒<br />\n我上個星期去剝隻智慧齒<br />\n反而剝完牙冇發燒</blockquote><br />\n 我差唔多成年 到宜家都未剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}